title: Allows pinch zoom on full screen images.
message:
Allows pinch zoom on full screen images.

Also to note. Due an issue with my computer I have had to change the
package name from `droidotter` to `otterdroid` as I have to create a new
Play Store listing as I no longer have access to the signing key.

More information can be found on Pjuu.com and the F-Droid forums.

title: Links that are not "pjuu.com" links are now opened in the default browser via an Intent. Closes #1.
message: Links that are not "pjuu.com" links are now opened in the default browser via an Intent. Closes #1.

title: Fixes for a few things...
message:
Fixes for a few things...

Closes #3 - Javascript confirmation requires WebChromeClient to be set. It is now set with an empty subclass called PjuuWebChromeClient, this will be needed to fix other issues.

Closes #4 - Back button leaving the application in certain circumstances. This is noticable if you open an image in full view (press the image when viewing a post not in a list). This is now overridden with onKeyDown and onBackPressed.

Sorted out Gradle settings for newer Android Studio. Not worked on this for a while and it was complaining.

title: Dropped version to 0.1.
message:
Dropped version to 0.1.

I was doing this in the manifest and it was not taking effect. I got confused. Turns out this is controlled by Gradle these days.

message: A few tweaks to Manifest and .gitignore

title: Cleaned up failures for GET requests...
message:
Cleaned up failures for GET requests...

We can't do it for POSTs because we can't catch them with WebView or WebViewClient. We will have to come up with a solution to this.

Added a spinner when the page is loading for a bit of visual feed back.

This will be the first released version of the Android app.
